description: So simple, a tasty meat free and budget friendly meal for two.
keywords: Roasted Pumpkin Spinach & Toasted Pine Nut Pasta
name: Roasted Pumpkin Spinach & Toasted Pine Nut Pasta Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Add olive oil and garlic to large pan and heat on low heat for a few minutes. Then turn up heat and add the pasta, pumpkin, spinach and black pepper and toss together until heated through thoroughly. Plate up and sprinkle toasted pine nuts on top. Enjoy!
